quran[39]{c,v,t}:
  23,36,"“Ili kwanaula, ili kwanaula yankupedwa chilangayo (nganiiŵa itendekwe ata panandi).”"
  23,37,"“Pangali (umi) wine ikaŵeje umi wetu waduniyapeuno, tukuwaga, nambo soni tukulamaga, soni nganituŵa uwwe ŵanti ni kuukulidwa m’malembe.”"
  23,38,"“Nganijuŵa aju (jwaakuliŵilanjila utumeju) ikaŵeje mundu jwansepele Allah unami, soni uwwe nganituŵa tunkulupilile jwalakwe.”"
  23,39,"(Hudu) jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Munjenjelani ligongo lyakunganila.”"
  23,40,"(Allah) jwatite: “Pangakaŵapa taŵe ŵakuligamba.”"
  23,41,"Basi ni wakwembekenye n’gumilo (waipotesi) mwakuonaonape, basi ni twatesile kuŵa mpela iswani (yakujigalwa ni mesi), basi chonasiko chakunaula chaliji kwa ŵandu ŵalupuso"
  23,42,Kaneko twagumbile panyuma pao mikutula jine
  23,43,Pangali umati wampaka ujijanguye kapena kujichelewasya ndema jakwe (jakuwila)
  23,44,"Kaneko twatumisye achimitenga Ŵetu mwakuyana. Ndema ni katema kajwauŵichililaga umati uliose ntenga jwakwe ŵankanilaga, ni twaakuyichisyaga ŵane panyuma pa ŵane (wa kuchonasiko), ni twatesile ŵanganyao kuŵa ngani (sisyesyene syaŵandu ŵakala syakwajamuka nasyo ŵandu ŵasambano), basi chonasiko chakunaula chaliji kwa ŵandu ŵangakulupilila"
  23,45,"Kaneko twantumisye Musa ni nkulugwe Haruna, pamo ni isimosimo Yetu kwisa soni umboni wakuonechela"
  23,46,"Kwa Firiauna ni nduna syakwe, nambo ŵanganyao ŵalikwesyisye ni ŵaliji soni ŵandu ŵakulinyakula"
  23,47,"Basi ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ana twakulupilile ŵandu ŵaŵili ŵanti mpela uwwewe, kutendaga ŵandu ŵao kukwetu ali achikapolo!”"
  23,48,"Mwanti ŵaakaaniile ŵanaŵaŵilio, basi ni ŵaliji (akukanilao) mwa akonanjidwa"
  23,49,Soni chisimu Uwwe twampele Musa Chitabu kuti ŵanganyao ajongoche
  23,50,"Soni twantesile Mwanache jwa Maryam kwisa soni Mamagwe kuŵa chisimosimo (chakulosya ukombosi Wetu, wakomboleka ŵakongwe kuŵeleka mwanache mwangali kusimana ni ŵalume), ni twajuyiye ŵanaŵaŵilio pachikwesya chakutamilichika ni ntunjelele, chachakwete soni achitutumule (pa Baitul Muqaddas)"
  23,51,E jenumanja achimitenga! Lyagani yakulya yambone ni mpanganyeje ichindu yambone. Chisimu Une ichindu yankutenda mbele Jwaimanya chenene
  23,52,"Soni chisimu awu nkutula wenu (wa Usilamu) ni nkutula umpepe, soni Une ni Nam’mbuje gwenu, basi njogopani"
  23,53,"Nambo (akwakuya achimitengao) ŵanupulanilene dini jao chilikati chao ni kuŵa mikutulamikutula, likuga lililyose pachikulupi chalinacho akasachisengwelaga"
  23,54,"Basi mwalekani ŵanganyao mu kusokonechela mwaomo, kwikanila ndema (jao jakuwila)"
  23,55,Ana akuganichisya yanti chipanje ni ŵanache yatukwapa mwawinji
  23,56,"Kuti tukwaŵilinganya pakwapa yambone? (Ngwamba, kweleko kwalechelesya pa duniya pano, kuti akaja kupata yambone iliyose ku Akhera), nambo kuti ngakulimanyilila"
  23,57,Chisimu aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkuligandasya ligongo lyakun’jogopa M’mbuje gwao
  23,58,Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkugakulupilila ma Ȃya ga M’mbuje gwao
  23,59,Ni aŵala ŵangaakum’bwanganya M’mbuje gwao (ni isanamu)
  23,60,"Ni aŵala ŵaakutolaga (Zaka ni sadaka syao), syaakupelekaga aku mitima jao jili ni woga (wanti itendo yaoyo mwine ipocheledwe kapena iyayi), ligongo lyanti ŵanganyao ali ni chikulupi chanti kwa M’mbuje gwao tachiujila (ni kuja kuŵalanjidwa itendo yao)"
  23,61,"Ŵanganyao ni ŵaakutenda chitema pa ichindu yambone, soni ŵanganyao pa yalakweyo akuŵa paujo (mpela kuswali ipindi kundanda kwandaŵi syakwe)"
  23,62,"Soni ngatukunkanganikaga mundu (kutenda) ikaŵeje yampaka ayikombole, soni Kukwetu kwana Chitabu chakuŵecheta yakuonaonape (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfūz), soni ŵanganyao ngasaja kutendedwa lupuso"
  23,63,"Nambo mitima jao (achimakafilio) jili mupupulipupuli wa aji (Qur’an), soni akwete ŵanganyao itendo yangaŵaga yalakwe (yaisalidwe kwa ŵakulupilila) yataŵe ŵanganyao ali nkuipanganya"
  23,64,"Kwikanila ndema jatuchakwembekanya ŵakulipatila ŵao ni ilagasyo, jele ndemajo ŵanganyao tachigumila pakuŵenda chikamuchisyo"
  23,65,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Ngasin’gumila pakuŵenda chikamuchisyo lelo, chisimu ŵanganyammwe nganchenjeledwa Nowe.”"
  23,66,"“Chisimu ma Ȃya Gangu galiji nkusoomedwa kukwenu, nambo mwaliji nkugalauchila ku indende yenu (pakugakanila galakwe).”"
  23,67,"“Aku n’di nkulikwesya (ligongo lyanti ŵakutama pa Nsikiti Wakuchimbichika wa Maaka), n’di nkuŵechetana chilo yangalumbana yaajigamba jalakwe (Qur’an).”"
  23,68,"Ana nganalicheteleleje ŵanganyao liloŵe (lya Allah lyalitulusyidwe kwa Muhammadi ﷺ jajili Qur’an), kapena yaichilile yanganiyaichilileje achatati ŵao ŵandanda"
  23,69,"Kapena nganammanya ntenga jwao (ndamo syakwe syambone), basi ŵanganyao jwalakwe ni akunkana"
  23,70,"Kapena akutiji: “Mwajwalakwe mwana masoka!” (Ngwamba), nambo kuti jwaichilile ni yakuona, soni ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao yakuona akuichimaga.Sano ingaŵe kuti yakuona yakuyiye isako yao, nikuti gakajonasiche mawunde ni mataka kwisa soni yaili mwalakwemo, nambo kuti Uwwe twaichilile ŵanganyao ni chikumbusyo chao, sano ŵanganyao yachikumbusyo chaocho akunyosyela"
  23,71,"Sano ingaŵe kuti yakuona yakuyiye isako yao, nikuti gakajonasiche mawunde ni mataka kwisa soni yaili mwalakwemo, nambo kuti Uwwe twaichilile ŵanganyao ni chikumbusyo chao, sano ŵanganyao yachikumbusyo chaocho akunyosyela"
  23,72,"Kapena mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkwajuga ŵanganyao malipilo (ni ligongo lyakwe akujikana Diniji)? Nambotu malipilo ga Ambuje ŵenu ni gagali gambone nnope, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwambone nnope mwa akupeleka lisiki"
  23,73,Soni chisimu mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkwaŵilanjila ŵanganyao kwitala lyagoloka
  23,74,Soni chisimu aŵala ŵangakukulupilila ya Akhera akusepuchila kwanaula kuleka litala (lyagolokalyo)